---
layout: base-layout
title: What have I been reading?
---

<section>
  <h2>{{ title }}</h2>
  <p>
    I'll be keeping track of what I've been reading here, and hopefully I'll
    share my thoughts a bit too.
  </p>
  <p>
    Books are listed in the order I finished them, if I didn't finish a library
    book, I probably had to return it before I was done ðŸ˜…
  </p>
</section>

<section class="book-list">
  <details>
    <summary>
      What kind of books did I finish each for year I've been tracking?
    </summary>
    {% for year in bookList.yearlyReadList %} {% if year.total > 0 %}
    <details>
      <summary>{{ year.label }} - {{ year.total }} total books</summary>
      <ul>
        {% for category, count in year.categories %}
        <li>{{ count }} {{ category }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </details>
    {% endif %} {% endfor %}
  </details>
</section>
<section class="book-list">
  {% for month in bookList.sortedBookList %}
  <h3>{{ month[0].dateLabel }}</h3>
  <ul>
    {% for book in month %}
    <li>
      <div>
        {{ book.title }} - {{ book.authours }} {% if book.post %} -
        <a href="{{ book.post }}">Read what I think</a>.{% endif %}
      </div>
      {% if book.rating %}
      <div>
        {% for i in range(1,6) %} {% if book.rating >= i %} â˜… {% else %} â˜† {%
        endif %} {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %} {% booktag book.tags %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
